data.value: Welcome to our simulation tool. the sole purpose of this tool is to evaluate the metrics of a queue based system with vacancy policy N we assume that in our system the packets arrive with different priority classes this simulation is a discrete event based on the event planning approach The manly performances are : 1- Energy Consumption. 2- Mean waiting time. 3- Mean response time. 4- Blocking probability. 5- Vacancy probability
